better come out right now

44:45.884 --> 44:48.920
Sorry, sorry, it's just me.

44:48.954 --> 44:51.156
Just Ronnie.

44:51.189 --> 44:54.926
Ronnie, what are you
doing in the woods?

44:55.794 --> 44:59.130
Oh I just saw the fire
and I heard voices, so

45:03.769 --> 45:06.137
Why don't you join us?

45:07.939 --> 45:10.942
